### 1. NVIDIA Source Code License — Mix Transformer (`mit.py`)

The file `code/Model/mit.py` is derived from [NVlabs/SegFormer](https://github.com/NVlabs/SegFormer) (`mmseg/models/backbones/mix_transformer.py`), which is licensed under the **NVIDIA Source Code License**.

