> Commercial use requires a separate license agreement with NVIDIA.

**Affected model**: `Segformer-b3` (SegFormer MIT-B3 encoder).

### 2. ImageNet-22k Pretrained Weights

The following pretrained backbones were trained on **ImageNet-22k**, which was released for **non-commercial research purposes only**. The pretrained weights may carry **CC-BY-NC** (non-commercial) restrictions:

| Weight | Affected Model | Restriction |
|--------|---------------|-------------|
| `swin_small_patch4_window7_224_22k.pth` | SwinV1-Small | ImageNet-22k: non-commercial research |
